title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 10 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 10 2022
description:
Biden approval down to 41% in CNN poll. Biden claims BBB is fully paid for, shifts to health care. Clay had opened the show by saying, "It appears Build Back Better is dead." MSNBC libs now to the left of Rev. Al on crime. Arkansas Senate candidate and former NFL player Jake Bequette hangs with C&B, talks Super Bowl and politics. C&B preview Friday's show and take some calls to close out today's program.
